{"tid":911905,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無人提？] 美國貿易代表署發表「301條款」調查報告更新版","createTime":"2018-11-22T09:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T11:22:56.000Z","uid":62646,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"420c395c81041dba2fbcad89b7dd8292027b0fd2","tid":911905,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:20:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2213892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2213892&d=%2FXlLKxHMo%2FigLamPEfJo7MKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=0911e5d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2213892</a><br />\n<br />\n距習特會僅約10天，白宮對華鷹派總動員施壓。美國貿易代表署（USTR）發表「301條款」調查報告更新版，指中國在強制技術轉移、竊取知識產權、貿易不公問題上「變本加厲」。白宮首席經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）更指，倘美中在華盛頓的磋商計劃落空，美中將於G20峰會攤牌<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表署發表報告稱，中國未改變處於中美貿易衝突核心的「不公平」做法，中國有關技術轉移、知識產權和創新的行為、政策和做法變本加厲，沒有對301條款調查報告作出建設性的反應，也沒有採取任何實際行動解決美國關注的問題。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特希澤（Robert Lighthizer）在聲明中表示，這份報告表明，中國並沒有從根本上改變其不公平、不合理且扭曲市場的做法，這些都是美方今年3月發表301條款調查報告中的主題。<br />\n<br />\n份report<br />\n<a href=\"https://ustr.gov/about-us/policy-offices/press-office/press-releases/2018/november/ustr-updates-section-301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fustr.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fpolicy-offices%2Fpress-office%2Fpress-releases%2F2018%2Fnovember%2Fustr-updates-section-301&d=%2FXlLKxHMo%2FigLamPEfJo7MKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=8bb3b953\" target=\"_blank\">https://ustr.gov/about-us/policy-offices/press-office/press-releases/2018/november/ustr-updates-section-301</a>"},{"pid":"49fe914146f3519c0691b6d225bc8cc2dc806ebb","tid":911905,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bd4982f88d0baf46352bd9f55c56fb7b7eb905","tid":911905,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"等多d人知道發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3795df3599d4cbb5d2654601fd3f25960c0697a","tid":911905,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8866410949d118efde623e1dcd1ab0faa96b2dcd","tid":911905,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"川習會登場前 美301調查報告再批中<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/910096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/910096</a><br />\n<br />\n提左"},{"pid":"4be8b9de300d203a48558746dfed39c160dc227d","tid":911905,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份野語氣超重<br />\n<br />\nVI. Conclusion<br />\nAs the evidence gathered in this update demonstrates, <strong>China fundamentally has not altered its acts, policies, and practices related to technology transfer, intellectual property, and innovation,<br />\nand<span style=\"color: red;\"> indeed appears to have taken further unreasonable actions in recent months.</strong> </span>USTR intends to continue its efforts to monitor any new developments and actions in this area."},{"pid":"830c6bfefa52a360b90dcaacb9d880c1ed9b5b18","tid":911905,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31dff1094dd1ce0410d4f51259f431a64853a75c","tid":911905,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ced2d6e7c472ae6ed44e2d7e4063de138eb5e2","tid":911905,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"距習特會僅約10天，白宮對華鷹派總動員施壓。美國貿易代表署（USTR）發表「301條款」調查報告更新版，指中國在強制技術轉移、竊取知識產權、貿易不公問題上<span style=\"color: red;\">「變本加厲</span>」。白宮首席經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）更指，倘美中在華盛頓的磋商計劃落空，<span style=\"color: red;\">美中將於G20峰會攤牌</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5691a9ab3b82684e1c01c7e7fffcd8fee1606334","tid":911905,"uid":23180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"吹咩美國人誤解香港、戴有色眼鏡果班唔該學下野，睇下人地講野唔係立亂講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個report應該有識中文人幫拖，仲睇穿你班共匪以為唔講2025無人知，去睇下第7頁開始就講知道你地班撚樣對外唔講2025但就繼續照做，財政同政策上有埋Evidence推論你繼續推緊(所以話作為普通人應該繼續幫共匪宣傳2025)，由第7頁開始都係講共匪對不公平貿易嘅狀況繼續Keep住做，仲列埋係歐盟、日本、澳洲偷左D咩，清清楚楚報告出黎。<br />\n<br />\n仲有成班支國企俾人Check倒網絡襲擊同去Hack人，好老實幾時制裁埋佢地???<br />\n<br />\nConclusion仲要話你班共匪態度照舊繼續無改:<br />\nAs the evidence gathered in this update demonstrates, China fundamentally has not altered its acts, policies, and practices related to technology transfer, intellectual property, and innovation, and indeed appears to have taken further unreasonable actions in recent months. USTR intends to continue its efforts to monitor any new developments and actions in this area.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fba094265b0bbe1d58cb53f15b2b219969207d","tid":911905,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a817b916a2559790a59f9e1921d9eb45369bd08b","tid":911905,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20